{"tid":1170264,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［引渡惡法］美國誇黨派議員去信林鄭促撤草案","createTime":"2019-05-25T01:45:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-25T02:00:08.000Z","uid":56537,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"03b7afb9fe9f958fda435e4fd4e840e4fd001e85","tid":1170264,"uid":56537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T01:45:59.000Z","msg":"美國8名參眾兩院的跨黨派議員聯署去信特首林鄭月娥，要求特區政府撤回修訂《逃犯條例》。信中指憂慮修例後將影響目前美國與香港之間的關係，草案一旦通過，將不可挽回地損害香港的高度自治和對人權的保護，並容許中國政府引渡居於香港商人、記者、人權倡議者以及異見人士。<br />\n<br />\n信中又指出，《逃犯條例》修訂通過後，美國及其他跨國企業可能選擇將總部，由香港遷往亞太其他地區一個「不會將外國公民置於引渡到中國大陸的風險之中」的城市。<br />\n<br />\n聯署的8名議員中，有7名早前出席於美國國會召開，針對香港人權狀況的聽證會。香港眾志亦轉載有關信件，指今次致特首的信函相當少見，印證了「逃犯條例」修訂極之嚴峻的狀況。<br />\n<br />\n8名聯署議員名單<br />\n<br />\n&bull; Massachusetts Congressman Jim McGovern 民主黨眾議員<br />\n&bull; Florida Senator Marco Rubio 共和黨參議員<br />\n&bull; New Jersey Congressman Chris Smith 共和黨眾議員<br />\n&bull; Montana Senator Steve Daines 共和黨參議員<br />\n&bull; New York Congressman Thomas Suozzi 民主黨眾議員<br />\n&bull; Arkansas Senator Tom Cotton 共和黨參議員<br />\n&bull; Florida Congressman Brian Mast 共和黨眾議員<br />\n&bull; Utah Congressman Ben McAdams 民主黨眾議員<br />\n<br />\n777真係勁到團結民主共和兩黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6b2ce9ea7f77a9b4f9fcaab0767143bf3190e9f","tid":1170264,"uid":56537,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T01:50:50.000Z","msg":"八名有來自民主共和兩黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nTrump trump快d出聲幫拖話中國除非版權外，對香港事務干預啦，直頭制裁支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2120f9e9b8dcbabc8d3f83b81880615c8d86aaf","tid":1170264,"uid":56537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a6b2ce9ea7f77a9b4f9fcaab0767143bf3190e9f","tid":1170264,"uid":56537,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T01:50:50.000Z","msg":"八名有來自民主共和兩黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nTrump trump快d出聲幫拖話中國除非版權外，對香港事務干預啦，直頭制裁支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T01:51:46.000Z","msg":"除<span style=\"color: red;\">左</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac73a54fa168139a6059188f21da40a4513c9ebf","tid":1170264,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T01:52:57.000Z","msg":"團結美國<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94efc3616cde1e7b68de53c53038f90d4c32a2ed","tid":1170264,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ac73a54fa168139a6059188f21da40a4513c9ebf","tid":1170264,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T01:52:57.000Z","msg":"團結美國<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T01:53:58.000Z","msg":"團結埋歐盟 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0e0a4205e7e85ef9104bbd272b67175f560c4d4","tid":1170264,"uid":56537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"94efc3616cde1e7b68de53c53038f90d4c32a2ed","tid":1170264,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ac73a54fa168139a6059188f21da40a4513c9ebf","tid":1170264,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T01:52:57.000Z","msg":"團結美國<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T01:53:58.000Z","msg":"團結埋歐盟 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T01:55:16.000Z","msg":"團結歐美 聯軍"},{"pid":"bb987175b27ff59bd4a6e14f8639e05863a3bdd7","tid":1170264,"uid":212246,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"ac73a54fa168139a6059188f21da40a4513c9ebf","tid":1170264,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"